                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17921215-23-defend351 t17921215-23-punish143"></join>
               fined 1 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Baron PERRYN.</p>
